			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>there is absolutely nothing wrong with using an unordered list for Q&amp;A&#8217;s, I think they look much neater than definition lists. To suggest that definition lists are the best way to go, suggests that you have something stuck somewhere it doesn&#8217;t belong. I would also suggest that you get your tags correct before assuming that you have anything worthwhile to teach.</p>
